snippet.title: Generation Exile - Official Gameplay Trailer | PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Check out a look at gameplay for Generation Exile, a survival game all about creating a society and adjusting to the ecosystem on a new planet.

Generation Exile is coming soon to PC.
